('FORMATION: Les micro-certifications (badges digitaux) augmentent la completion des formations de 35%.', 'Micro-certifications badges = +35% completion formation', NULL, 'insight', 0.80, 'massive_boost_19', 'system'),
('FORMATION: Le format cohort-based (cohorte avec dates fixes + communaute) a 10x plus de completion que le self-paced.', 'Cohort-based = 10x completion vs self-paced', NULL, 'insight', 0.82, 'massive_boost_19', 'system'),
